TopicTitle: Problem exporting part to KSP from Blender

Articles.Content:
Trying to make a lander leg, however it won\'t load. I followed the blender tutorial, but I\'m sure I did something wrong. Does anybody know what the problem is? Any help would be much appreciated. I\'m just trying to get it in-game currently, I\'ll make it attach to the side later.

Thanks!

-Mincespy
You have the wrong .DAE name in you part.cfg file. Fix it and it loads ok.
